programs.program:
as principal admin password "admin" do
set records = []
append to records with "ike"
append to records with "andy"
append to records with "ally"
local names = records
foreach rec in names replacewith concat("m",rec)
local splits = names
foreach rec in splits replacewith split(rec,"....")
foreach rec in splits replacewith rec.snd
local filters = splits
filtereach rec in filters with rec
filtereach rec in names with notequal(rec,"mike")
append to records with names
append to records with splits
append to records with filters
return records
***
